data.description: Great price and great deal in Voss Farms!  Complete with a finished out Shed (Man Cave or She Shed?), this 3/2 has a nice open plan with a large kitchen.  Tall ceilings make the home feel even roomier!  You are going to love the HUGE and PRIVATE backyard with a giant covered back porch.  Neighborhood amenities include 2 pools, clubhouse, and walking trails!
